Package: scRnaCnv
Type: Package
Title: A package to help stream together multiple scRNA-seq inference tools
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Rene Quevedo
Maintainer: Rene Quevedo <quever88@gmail.com>
Description: This package intends to integrate and stream together scRNA-seq
  CNV inference tools. The main purpose is to create a simple pipeline to 
  run one of several different cnv invference tools (e.g. HoneyBADGER, 
  inferCNV, etc..) using default parameters from a command line interface
  with minimal amount of user intervention. Extended goals are to refine
  CNV calls using multiple callers to identify robustness of CNV calls.
